text: Students with Saturday classes be like #MayPasokBa #WalangPasok #GardoPH #HenryPH #SaturdayVibes #SaturdayThoughts

In just three days, STY #Hinnamnor (#HenryPH) now has the highest Accumulated Cyclone Energy (ACE) by any tropical cyclone in the Western Pacific basin this 2022, with 19.1 (as of 00 UTC, September 1). It has surpassed TY #Malakas last April, with ACE of 17.0.

Iâ€™ve been alerted of Signal No. 8 making rounds on socmed. 1. There are only 5 Wind Signals used by  @dost_pagasa.  2. While Signal No. 5 is for Super Typhoon, #HenryPH is non-landfalling. PAGASA clarified today that the highest wind signal that may be raised is Signal No. 3.

Typhoon #HenryPH is now accelerating northward whie maintaining its strength. At 10 a.m. today, it was located 405 km Northeast of Itbayat, Batanes, with max winds of 150 kph and gusts up to 185 kph. It may exit the PAR tonight.
